Sentencas: Architectonics of the paper-structured catalyst for the application to the biofuel reformer or direct internal reforming SOFC (DIRSOFC) was studied.
Titulo: Paper-structured catalyst for the steam reforming of biodiesel fuel

Sentencas: Inorganic fiber network, paper, composed of yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) fiber (Zf), alumina fiber (Af) and inorganic binder (Al2O3 sol (As) or ZrO2 sol (Zs) or CeO2 sol (Cs)) was prepared by a simple paper-making process.
Titulo: Paper-structured catalyst for the steam reforming of biodiesel fuel

Sentencas: Then, the catalytic activities of the Ni and Ni-MgO loaded papers called paper-structured catalysts (PSCs) for the steam reforming of biodiesel fuels (BDFs) were evaluated.
Titulo: Paper-structured catalyst for the steam reforming of biodiesel fuel

Sentencas: Ni-MgO loaded PSC using Cs as an inorganic binder, Ni-MgO/ZfAfCs, exhibited excellent performance over Ru/gamma Al2O3 catalyst beads.
Titulo: Paper-structured catalyst for the steam reforming of biodiesel fuel

Sentencas: Formation of light hydrocarbons, especially C2H4, was eliminated and water gas shift reaction was more promoted compared to the catalyst beads.
Titulo: Paper-structured catalyst for the steam reforming of biodiesel fuel
